data.text:
Owen Wilson is expecting his second child, US Magazine reports.

Gallery: Check out the biggest celebrity feuds

Wilson will welcome baby No. 2 with his personal trainer Caroline Lindqvist, who is currently divorcing her husband. Although Wilson and Lindqvist are not actually a couple, he plans to support her through the pregnancy and be there for their child.

Wilson is already father to Robert Ford, 2, with ex-girlfriend Jade Duell.
